l-Sage grants a d8 to a creature within 30 ft. of it. The creature can roll the d8 and add the result to its next ability check or saving throw.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"long":30,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668072948055,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"ZLjJISMkPwtyCfav","name":"Decelerate.","type":"feat","sort":600000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/37.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Decelerate.</strong> A creature within 40 ft. of the Shell-Sage must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw or be affected by ability for its duration. An affected target’s speed is halved, it takes a −2 penalty to AC and Dexterity saving throws, and it can’t use reactions. On its turn, it can use either an action or a bonus action, not both. Regardless of the creature’s abilities or magic items, it can’t make more than one melee or ranged attack during its turn. If the creature attempts to cast a spell with a casting time of 1 action, roll a d20. On an 11 or higher, the spell doesn’t take effect until the creature’s next turn, and the creature must use its action on that turn to complete the spell. If it can’t, the spell is wasted. Only one creature at a time can be affected by this ability.</p><p><br /></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":40,"long":40,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668072827629,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"HNciPtDhZuHJ4xUB","name":"Invoke Contemplation.","type":"feat","sort":700000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/spellbook04_94.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Invoke Contemplation.</strong> A creature within 40 ft. of the Shell-Sage must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw or be put in a state of contemplative trance.</p><div><p></p></div><p>An affected target can’t take reactions and must roll a d8 at the start of each of its turns to determine its behavior for that turn.</p><div><p></p></div><p><strong>1:</strong> The creature attempts to share its contemplative thoughts with its allies. If an allied creature is within 15 ft. of the affected creature, the allied creature must succeed on a DC 15 saving throw or be affected by this ability as well.</p><div><p></p></div><p><strong>2-4:</strong> The creature is lost in contemplative thoughts and doesn’t move or take actions this turn.</p><div><p></p></div><p><strong>5-7:</strong> The creature contemplates the situation and opts for a non-violent solution, either attempting to convince allies to do the same or leave, using its movement to move away from the Shell-Sage and continueing to do so until its is no longer affected or takes damage from the Shell-Sage or its allies.</p><div><p></p></div><p><strong>8:</strong> The creature comes to the conclusion that it is quite happy with how things are going and can act normally this turn.</p><div><p></p></div><p>At the end of its turns, an affected target can repeat the Wisdom saving throw, ending the effect on itself. Only one creature at a time can be affected by this ability.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":40,"long":40,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"wis","dc":null,"scaling":"wis"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668073617165,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"AM3EpIhoX8LCs45K","name":"Shell Fortress","type":"feat","sort":800000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/spellbook04_17.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Shell Fortress.</strong> The Shell-Sage withdraws into its shell, gaining a +5 bonus to its AC. It can use Spiritual Guidance and Endure while inside its shell, but no other actions. It can emerge from its shell as a bonus action on its turn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"self","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668073519964,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"Wz4Ve73hiQO6p8KU","name":"Endure","type":"feat","sort":900000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/blue_33.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<div><p><strong>Endure.</strong> If the Shell-Sage is subjected to an effect that allows it to make a Dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, it can its reaction to make a Constitution saving throw instead, taking no damage if it succeeds on the saving throw, interposing its mighty shell between itself and the source of the effect.</p><div><p></p></div></div><p></p><p></p><p> </p><div><p></p></div><p> </p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668073232598,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"XwmOq1tyWF0BgNJs","name":"Mindful Presence","type":"feat","sort":1000000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/spellbook06_07.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Mindful Presence.</strong> Creatures within 15 ft. of the Shell-Sage make saving throws to end conditions they are affected by with advantage.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668072996876,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"BvuxWjIUZ3A1856c","name":"Slow and Purposeful","type":"feat","sort":1100000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/r_46.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Slow and Purposeful.</strong> The Shell-Sage’s movement is unaffected by difficult terrain.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668073662757,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}},{"_id":"JSxGpz0BNrIJq3LD","name":"Oblivious Luck","type":"feat","sort":1200000,"flags":{},"img":"beneos_tokens_assets//_ability_icons/spellbook03_44.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Oblivious Luck.</strong> Any creature who targeting the Shell-Sage with an attack or a harmful spell must first make a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature must choose a new target or lose the attack or spell. This doesn’t protect the Shell-Sage from area effects. If a creature succeeds on the saving throw, it is immune to the effect of this ability for 24 hours. If the Shell-Sage targets a creature with an attack, this creature also gains immunity to the effect for 24 hours.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Beneos Tokens","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":1668073498391,"lastModifiedBy":"7ptJY7RGU63YcaB9"}}],"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Actor.Gd9zhB8mXwuLtY3s"},"exportSource":{"world":"beneos-tokens-setup-world","system":"dnd5e","coreVersion":"10.288","systemVersion":"2.0.3"}},"system":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":16,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}},"dex":{"value":6,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}},"con":{"value":20,"proficient":1,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}},"int":{"value":14,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}},"wis":{"value":20,"proficient":1,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}},"cha":{"value":18,"proficient":0,"bonuses":{"check":"","save":""}}},"attributes":{"ac":{"flat":18,"calc":"natural","formula":""},"hp":{"value":127,"min":0,"max":127,"temp":null,"tempmax":0,"formula":"13d8+65"},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0},"movement":{"burrow":0,"climb":0,"fly":0,"swim":0,"walk":15,"units":"ft","hover":false},"attunement":{"max":3},"senses":{"darkvision":0,"blindsight":0,"tremorsense":0,"truesight":0,"units":"ft","special":""},"spellcasting":"int"},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<h1>How to run a Shell-Sage</h1><div><p></p></div><h3><strong>1. Offensively.</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Decelerate</strong> and  <strong>Invoke Contemplation</strong> are not offensive per se, but can be used to hinder or even disable key enemies for a while.</p></li><li><p>On its turn, the Sage should always use <strong>Spiritual Guidance</strong> on an ally or even itself (as it is a creature within 30 ft. of itself) and use their action to go for either <strong>Contemplation</strong> or <strong>Decelerate.</strong> </p></li><li><p>The <strong>Sage's Staff</strong> should be used very sparingly, as it doesn't do much and because Shell-Sages are kind of averse to violence.</p><div><p></p></div></li></ul><h3><strong>2. Defensively.</strong></h3><ul><li><p>The Sage is a big ol’ bundle of hit points and AC, hardy and sturdy as a humanoid turtle should be.</p><div><p></p></div></li><li><p><strong>Endure</strong> counters one of the biggest weaknesses of the Sage in an organic way, as it wouldn’t even try to dodge, but rather trust in its shell.</p><div><p></p></div></li><li><p><strong>Oblivious Luck</strong> is the third part to the puzzle, oftentimes forcing potential attackers to choose a different target to the Sage or even foregoing their attack. This does not make it invincible, but might keep some wolves at bay in a bind.</p><div><p></p></div></li><li><p>If all goes wrong, <strong>Shell Fortress</strong> paired with <strong>Endure</strong> and <strong>Oblivious Luck</strong> should keep the Sage from harm until rescued.</p></li></ul><div><p></p></div><h3><strong>3. General Notes</strong></h3><div><p></p></div><ul><li><p>The Shell-Sage is a fun and useful creature to accompany a party for a while, turning potential combat encounters into roleplaying opportunities due to Invoke Contemplation and buffing your players abilities with Spiritual Guidance.</p><div><p></p></div></li><li><p>Due to the sheer amount of hit points, paired with Endure and Shell Fortress, you don’t really have to worry about the Sage going down and wasting party resources, at least on lower and mid level.</p></li></ul>","public":""},"alignment":"Lawful Good","race":"","type":{"value":"humanoid","subtype":"","swarm":"","custom":""},"environment":"","cr":2,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":10},"source":"Beneos Tokens"},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"bypasses":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":[],"bypasses":[],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"bypasses":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":["common"],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"his":{"value":1,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"med":{"value":1,"ability":"wis","bonuses":{"check":"","passive":""}},"nat"